snippet.title: [ArcheWorld] Development Sneak Peek: NFT UCC
snippet.description:
Hello, Archeans!

We are happy to finally show you a little bit of the in-game world from ArcheWorld today. 

You can see the process of decorating your House with Fandom Card NFTs, as well as buying Land and building a House in this time’s Sneak Peek. I hope you enjoy it and please look forward to more Sneak Peek videos in the following weeks!

Thank you. 
*The video was taken in a development stage, and some changes may occur.
